- Document module and class variables (no docstrings, just show contents)
  (config option).
- Process signature overrides form 1st line of docstring for functions
  and methods.
- Nicer formatting for constructors.
- Add default link prefix, to resolve bare links to `attr` to `prefix.attr`
  (config option).
- Automatically resolve aliases in links, e.g. when linking to `module.attr`
  where `attr` is imported from `module.foo`, the link should resolve to
  `module.foo.attr` (config option).
